description:
JazzTimes In Person interview with pianist, composer and bandleader Michel Camilo from backstage at the 2011 Newport Jazz Festival, presented by Natixis.  In this segment, Camilo talks about playing with a big band and with a concert orchestra.

This segment is one of several done with Camilo and other musicians who were performing at the Newport Jazz Festival.

Interview by Lee Mergner. Video by Melissa Mergner.

For more information about JazzTimes magazine, go to jazztimes.com.
